This insurance contract, issued by Centriq Insurance Company Limited, is a health insurance policy for an individual named Fred Angasisye with policy number KH41314, effective from July 1, 2023, and renewing on January 1, 2025. The policy is administered by Umcebo Financial Services (Pty) Ltd.

The policy provides coverage for day-to-day medical expenses, including nurse consultations in Clicks or Dis-Chem Clinics, telephone or video consultations, and medication for acute or over-the-counter conditions listed in the policy. However, there is a six-month waiting period for chronic medicine related to type 2 diabetes and HIV.

Newborns or spouses added within 90 days of birth or marriage, or dependants added within 90 days of the policy start date, will not have waiting periods. The general waiting period can be waived if the insured party had at least three months of previous cover with no more than a two-month break before the policy start date. The condition-specific waiting period can be waived if the insured party had at least six months of previous cover with no more than a two-month break.
